OL,3,GEast Midlands
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FRather
OL,6,Fcloudy during the evening, with the
OL,7,Fodd spot of rain possible over the
OL,8,FPeak District. Becoming drier as the
OL,9,Fnight progresses, with lengthier clear
OL,10,Fperiods developing in southern areas
OL,11,Flater. Warmer than the previous night
OL,12,Fand feeling humid too.
OL,13,
OL,14,CMonday:FDry with hazy sunshine
OL,15,Finitially, the cloud gradually
OL,16,Fthickening from the west to give the
OL,17,Fodd shower late afternoon. Widely
OL,18,Fwarm, although cooler along coastal
OL,19,Fareas.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
